  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page\"> <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"products-title\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">產品系列</p> <h1 id=\"products-title\">兩類設備平台覆蓋光學分選與重型物料回收</h1> <p class=\"hero-copy\">比較 AI 可回收塑膠的光學分選系統，以及建築、裝飾、拆除及大型廢棄物專案的整合式 C&D 廢棄物回收處理線。</p></section> <section class=\"section product-family-intro\" id=\"product-comparison\" aria-labelledby=\"product-families-title\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">方案路徑</p> <h2 id=\"product-families-title\">產品匹配從物料流、場地限制與產出目標開始</h2> <p>其中一款產品家族專為高價值塑膠識別與光學分選而設計。另一類用於 C&D 及大型廢棄物專案中的重型破碎、篩選及資源化利用。</p></section> <section class=\"product-family-band product-family-ai\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-family-title\"> <div class=\"product-family-inner\"> <picture class=\"product-family-media\"> <img src=\"/assets/images/super-sorting.jpg\" alt=\"蔚澜超級光學分選系統配置與模組化分選設備\"></picture> <div class=\"product-family-content\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">超級光學分選系統</p> <h2 id=\"ai-family-title\">面向可回收塑膠的光學分選平台</h2> <p>模組化分選模組可依材質與顏色識別並區分 PET 瓶、HDPE 瓶、PP 及混合塑膠。</p> <div class=\"product-family-chips\" aria-label=\"典型材料\"> <span>PET 瓶</span> <span>HDPE 瓶</span> <span>PP 塑膠</span> <span>混合可回收物</span></div> <dl class=\"product-family-metrics\" aria-label=\"AI 光學分鏡亮點\"> <div> <dt>0.6-2 t/h</dt> <dd>吞吐量範圍</dd></div> <div> <dt>5-10</dt> <dd>物料類別</dd></div> <div> <dt>滑架模組</dt> <dd>更快的安裝</dd></div></dl> <p class=\"product-action-strip\"><a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/products/ai-optical-sorting\" aria-label=\"查看 AI 光學分選系統\">查看案例</a></p></div></div></section> <section class=\"product-family-band product-family-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"industrial-family-title\"> <div class=\"product-family-inner\"> <div class=\"product-family-content\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">建築與大型廢棄物預處理應用線</p> <h2 id=\"industrial-family-title\">一體化 C&D 廢棄物處置與資源化利用線</h2> <p>Lion One 一體化站面向重載破碎、骨料篩分與分離，結合穩定給料、破碎、骨料篩分、磁性分離、氣流分離及打包設備。</p> <div class=\"product-engineering-brief\"> <ol class=\"product-process-chain\" aria-label=\"核心 C&D 廢棄物處理流程\"> <li>穩定給料</li> <li>破碎</li> <li>骨料篩分</li> <li>磁分離</li> <li>氣流分離</li> <li>打包</li></ol> <dl class=\"product-line-specs\" aria-label=\"C&D 廢棄物線重點\"> <div> <dt>處理能力範圍</dt> <dd>20-70 t/h</dd></div> <div> <dt>單機使用範圍</dt> <dd>35 m<sup>2</sup></dd></div> <div> <dt>可調整破碎尺寸</dt> <dd>液壓驅動</dd></div></dl></div> <p class=\"product-action-strip\"> <a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/products/construction-waste-recycling-line\" aria-label=\"查看建築廢棄處理線產品資料\">查看案例</a></p></div> <picture class=\"product-family-media\"> <img src=\"/assets/images/lion-mark1.jpg\" alt=\"蔚澜建築與裝飾廢棄物的綜合破碎與篩選站\"></picture></div></section> <section class=\"contact-section\" aria-labelledby=\"products-inquiry-title\"> <div> <p class=\"eyebrow\">專案諮詢</p> <h2 id=\"products-inquiry-title\">廢棄物流、吞吐量、場地限制與專案階段越完整，產品匹配越準確</h2> <p>請分享你正在評估的廢棄物流、目標吞吐量、場址限制及專案階段。蔚澜可以推薦合適的產品系列，並準備更專注的提案討論。</p></div> <div class=\"about-contact-panel compact-contact-panel\"> <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求產品提案</a> <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/solutions\">查看解決方案路徑</a> <p>銷售熱線：+86 137 8001 2268 / +86 180 6737 7770</p></div></section> <section class=\"section\" id=\"specs\" aria-labelledby=\"specs-title\" hidden> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">產品資料</p> <h2 id=\"specs-title\">參數資料為型號對比提供清晰技術依據</h2></div> <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-ai\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-ai\"> <header class=\"spec-group-head\"> <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">超光學分選</span> <h3 id=\"spec-group-ai\">型號範圍由模組化光學分選配置定義</h3></header> <div class=\"spec-card-grid\"> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">迷你</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\"> <dt>處理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\"> <dt>動力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\"> <dt>佔地面積</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·8 × 3 m 版面 ·3 m 淨空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\"> <dt>分選範圍</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明 PET·有色 PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合塑膠\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">標準</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\"> <dt>處理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\"> <dt>動力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\"> <dt>佔地面積</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·12 × 3 m 版面 ·6 m 淨空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\"> <dt>分選範圍</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明 PET·綠 PET ·藍色 PET ·混色 PET·白 HDPE·有色 HDPE·PP ·混合塑膠·剔除\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 顏色 ·HDPE ·PP ·混合·剔除</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Plus</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\"> <dt>處理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\"> <dt>動力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\"> <dt>佔地面積</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·17 × 3 m 版面 ·6 m 淨空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <dt>分選範圍</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明 PET·綠 PET ·藍色 PET ·混色 PET·白 HDPE·有色 HDPE·PP ·PE ·混合塑膠·剔除\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 顏色 ·HDPE ·PP ·PE ·混合·剔除</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article></div></div> <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-cdw\"> <header class=\"spec-group-head\"> <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">C&D 廢棄物線</span> <h3 id=\"spec-group-cdw\">Lion One 一體化站</h3></header> <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\"> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">綜合破碎與篩選站</p></div> <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <div><dt>製造集團</dt><dd>蔚澜</dd></div> <div><dt>類型</dt><dd>移動站</dd></div> <div><dt>等級</dt><dd>重型&nbsp;</dd></div></dl></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>處理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">t/h</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>進料尺寸</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">mm</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>佔地面積</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">m<sup>2</sup> · 11.7 × 3 × 3.1 m</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>驅動</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">全液壓</span></dd></div></dl> <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span> <span>寧波，中國</span> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span> <span>整合移動站</span></footer></article></div></div></section></main>"
